7. DB-less Mode (Declarative Mode)

Kong can run without PostgreSQL database.

Configuration stored in YAML file.

Example:

_format_version: "3.0"

services:
  - name: echo-service
    url: http://localhost:8081
    routes:
      - name: echo-route
        paths:
          - /echo
Advantages
Easy deployment
Git version control
Fast startup
Great for Docker/Kubernetes